Package loginTests

Class FailedLoginTest

java.lang.Object
common.Browsers
loginTests.BaseTest
loginTests.FailedLoginTest
public class FailedLoginTest extends BaseTest
FailedLoginTest is a TestNG test class that tests the login functionality of the application when invalid credentials are entered. It uses the LoginMethods class to perform the login, and the DataProvider class to provide data for the test. It extends the BaseTest class.
